                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="gu-card-content">
                <h3>Activity Sheet 3</h3>
                <p class="gu-card-desc">Creative exercises connecting Kathiawadi dialect with Gujarat's unique grassland ecology.</p>
                <div class="gu-card-footer">
                    <a href="{{asset 'files/Resources/Alphabet Charts/Gujarati Alphabet Chart/Activity Sheet 3.pdf'}}" class="gu-download-btn" download>
                        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"></path><polyline points="7 10 12 15 17 10"></polyline><line x1="12" y1="15" x2="12" y2="3"></line></svg>
                        Download Resource
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Dynamic Cards from Ghost Admin (tag: gujarati-alphabet-chart) -->
        {{#get "posts" filter="tag:gujarati-alphabet-chart" limit="100" include="authors,tags"}}
            {{#foreach posts}}
                <div class="gu-card">
                    <div class="gu-card-img">
                        {{#if feature_image}}
                            <img src="{{img_url feature_image}}" alt="{{title}}">
                        {{/if}}
                        <div class="gu-card-overlay">
                            <a href="{{url}}" class="gu-overlay-link">
                                <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"></path><polyline points="7 10 12 15 17 10"></polyline><line x1="12" y1="15" x2="12" y2="3"></line></svg>
                                Quick View
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="gu-card-content">
                        <h3>{{title}}</h3>
                        <p class="gu-card-desc">{{excerpt}}</p>
                        <div class="gu-card-footer">
                            <a href="{{url}}" class="gu-download-btn">
                                <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"></path><polyline points="7 10 12 15 17 10"></polyline><line x1="12" y1="15" x2="12" y2="3"></line></svg>
                                View Resource
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            {{/foreach}}
        {{/get}}

    </div>

    <!-- Educator Note Section -->
    <section class="gu-educator-note-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="gu-educator-note-card">
                <div class="gu-educator-note-header">
                    <div class="gu-educator-icon">
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24" height="24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z"></path><path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h2 class="gu-educator-title">Note for Educators</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="gu-educator-content">
                    <p>This chart highlights unique local life — like wolves and indigenous breeds of livestock — that are essential to the region's ecology and pastoral culture. Developed collaboratively with pastoralists, botanists, and artists, this chart helps children and teachers discover the beauty, diversity, and cultural value embedded in Gujarat's grasslands. Use the accompanying activity sheets for structured, hands-on learning.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="gu-educator-activities">
                    <span class="gu-activities-title">Ways to Use</span>
                    <ul class="gu-activities-list">
                        <li>Display the chart in classrooms as a conversation starter about local grassland ecosystems</li>
                        <li>Use the activity sheets for individual or group exercises exploring Gujarat's biodiversity</li>
                        <li>Ask students to compare the organisms on the chart with ones they see in their own surroundings</li>
                        <li>Connect to EVS lessons about habitats, food chains, and pastoral livelihoods in Saurashtra</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Explore More Section -->
    <section class="gu-explore-more">
        <a href="/alphabet-charts/" class="gu-explore-btn">
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><line x1="19" y1="12" x2="5" y2="12"></line><polyline points="12 19 5 12 12 5"></polyline></svg>
            Explore More Alphabet Charts
        </a>
    </section>

</div>
